      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. every day its just more evidence that everything is collapsing. the planet is literally dying and we're all just pretending like we have a future. it feels so pointless to even try to build a life or care about anything when the end is already decided. what's even the point of any of it?",
